name: Eva-Maria Lemke
description:
A commission of @lemke. (Sorry I kept calling her "Ana", mate. xD)

Eva-Maria Lemke is a German journalist and tv anchorwoman.

1500-step TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with my usual settings. (Reduced learning rate to 0.002 after step 1000.)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
